Cars vs Angels is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the game or on our official website. Continued use of the game after changes take effect indicates acceptance of the revised policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

By downloading and playing Cars vs Angels, you agree to the collection and use of your data as outlined in this Privacy Policy.

